{"tid":1688980,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[以證視聽] 唔好再叫香港警狗 \"呀Sir\"、\"Madam\" 好嗎？","createTime":"2019-11-02T15:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T03:36:34.000Z","uid":34475,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c8221e830a0c52ef7ee2605de3a8b44a1f01225c","tid":1688980,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:44:49.000Z","msg":"Sir同Madam都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>尊稱</strong></span>黎<br />\n簡單蓋括係指長官/先生、夫人/女士<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今時今日你地唔係仲要尊重香港警狗下化？</span></span><br />\n香港警狗唔尊重我地，咁我地點解要尊重呢班垃圾狗呀<br />\n每次聽到見到我都好火滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你係想串佢都好，用個Sir字都係表示你覺得佢係高你一等既<br />\n宜家真．香港人，你係咪低下過香港警狗呀！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後見到香港警狗<br />\n不要說 &quot;呀Sir&quot;、&quot;Madam&quot;<br />\n試著說<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;呀警賊&quot;<br />\n&quot;曱甴&quot;<br />\n&quot;襟兄弟&quot;<br />\n&quot;垃圾&quot;<br />\n&quot;屌你老母食屎狗&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如有其他更適合和理非街坊屌狗既尊稱，歡迎提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家唔好再浪費尊重同禮貌向垃圾人種度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外想順便呼籲埋大家<br />\n唔好淨係幫襯出名既黃店，龍門呢d大排長龍夠人支持嫁啦，改懲罰下其他小黃店啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785f972851d0f096d78e38d7ebc3695bf5c2be43","tid":1688980,"uid":123765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"人地叫緊你曱甴，你仲叫人阿sir madam<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢d po又次次推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1eca1b52e9b5fff5e313cd5fe09db7e410abe0a","tid":1688980,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b57c10ee5e5df215e1c80bc2413fe8237758eb","tid":1688980,"uid":281180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:47:15.000Z","msg":"我每次聽到呢啲稱呼都好撚嬲，叫番佢哋做警員"},{"pid":"624583e6328236693f57394fd27f153ad28064be","tid":1688980,"uid":34475,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8b57c10ee5e5df215e1c80bc2413fe8237758eb","tid":1688980,"uid":281180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:47:15.000Z","msg":"我每次聽到呢啲稱呼都好撚嬲，叫番佢哋做警員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:49:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b88beea7b4686ae3ee0691def349318fa5c1d3f7","tid":1688980,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"曱甴公<br />\n曱甴乸"},{"pid":"c577daaaf90460e15b84e7e1b24eb5de0323fed9","tid":1688980,"uid":33868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"喂、差佬已經算好"},{"pid":"2fba910c56ab5a0567625415962007fd0508cf82","tid":1688980,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"講過好多次見過好多POST<br />\n但仲KEEP住聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba9be00f03ae7458ef6369176daae1e13dea0a6","tid":1688980,"uid":88725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"聽人講popo唔鐘意比人叫差佬<br />\n可以前面加個死字"},{"pid":"8cd7882bd5710eb1e147b10d7380ddb50afb328a","tid":1688980,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019